1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:03,140
[Episode 54]

2
00:00:12,810 --> 00:00:13,830
You know what?

3
00:00:14,030 --> 00:00:15,030
During this time

4
00:00:15,430 --> 00:00:17,550
