5
00:00:18,070 --> 00:00:20,550
I felt so happy

6
00:00:25,990 --> 00:00:27,190
Hey, Bin

7
00:00:30,790 --> 00:00:31,850
Who did this to you?

8
00:00:34,130 --> 00:00:35,390
Don't touch me

9
00:00:35,710 --> 00:00:36,630
I'm dirty

10
