12
00:00:39,270 --> 00:00:40,190
But those with dirty minds

13
00:00:40,190 --> 00:00:42,120
No amount of washing can clean that

14
00:00:42,270 --> 00:00:43,790
I'll tell the teachers right away

15
00:00:43,790 --> 00:00:44,990
And get them expelled

16
00:00:45,870 --> 00:00:47,350
These disgusting people

17
00:00:52,070 --> 00:00:52,530
Let's go

18
00:00:52,870 --> 00:00:53,800
Go wash yourself

19
00:01:04,030 --> 00:01:05,670
Why do your roses

20
00:01:05,790 --> 00:01:07,540
