Hey, Bin

24
00:01:16,910 --> 00:01:18,070
How did you get hurt?

25
00:01:18,550 --> 00:01:20,080
Was it those bullies again?

26
00:01:20,750 --> 00:01:21,470
No

27
00:01:21,550 --> 00:01:22,270
It's just that

28
00:01:22,270 --> 00:01:24,070
This finger got hurt

29
00:01:24,390 --> 00:01:25,550
