30
00:01:25,550 --> 00:01:27,350
So I taped them together

31
00:01:27,350 --> 00:01:28,750
So they could be a pair

32
00:01:30,750 --> 00:01:31,789
You scared me

33
00:01:33,110 --> 00:01:33,470
Here

34
00:01:33,830 --> 00:01:34,630
This is for you

35
00:01:35,470 --> 00:01:36,150
Thank you

36
00:01:39,190 --> 00:01:40,670
Can I eat this now?

37
00:01:40,950 --> 00:01:41,350
Yes

38
00:01:45,910 --> 00:01:46,550
Ouch

39
00:01:47,150 --> 00:01:47,950
What's wrong?

40
00:01:48,190 --> 00:01:50,070
My heart is being chewed up

41
00:01:50,310 --> 00:01:51,310
Haha

42
00:01:59,430 --> 00:02:00,070
Max

43
00:02:00,870 --> 00:02:01,470
Hmm?

44
00:02:02,030 --> 00:02:02,990
Um...

45
00:02:03,910 --> 00:02:05,030
Do you...

46
00:02:05,310 --> 00:02:06,150
Like me?

47
00:02:07,550 --> 00:02:08,270
Uh

48
00:02:08,590 --> 00:02:10,070
I don't know

49
00:02:12,710 --> 00:02:13,100
Well

50
00:02:13,140 --> 00:02:15,610
It's okay
If you don't like me

51
00:02:15,770 --> 00:02:17,690
Because I'm not pretty

52
00:02:18,010 --> 00:02:20,050
And you're a boy

53
00:02:20,490 --> 00:02:21,950
It's probably impossible

54
00:02:37,370 --> 00:02:38,090
Bin

55
00:02:39,170 --> 00:02:40,170
I think

56
00:02:41,050 --> 00:02:42,210
I like you

57
00:02:43,290 --> 00:02:43,930
Really?

58
00:03:01,690 --> 00:03:02,410
And I

59
00:03:02,770 --> 00:03:05,170
Don't want to lose moments like these again

60
00:03:05,340 --> 00:03:07,820
[To be continued]
